data.meta_description: ST01 - Zodiac.pdf - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document summarizes a meeting that took place on October 2nd, 1849 at the house of Mr. R-, a scholar. A group of disparate individuals had gathered, including two doctors, a colonel, two women, and a man named the Doctor along with his companions Ian and Barbara. Mr. R- hosted the gathering and introduced the guests. The purpose of the meeting was not disclosed to the narrator. Mr. R- then directed the guests' attention to the back room, implying the reason for the gathering would be revealed there.
